{"tid":2010484,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[行街寶寶注意] 班狗開始識設局聲東擊西 包抄手足","createTime":"2020-05-10T12:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T14:13:47.000Z","uid":98431,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"934641468095bfb4c099114b2a1acd10c9df223a","tid":2010484,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:18:43.000Z","msg":"班狗突然由鼓油街包抄西洋菜街<br />\n<br />\nKong Tsung-gan / 江松澗<br />\n@KongTsungGan<br />\nDozens of riot police &amp; raptors have just charged the hundreds gathered on Sai Yeung Choi St S <span style=\"color: red;\">from 2 directions in an attempt to trap them.</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Most escaped but I fear some didn&rsquo;t.</span> The move appears to be designed to extricate their colleagues trapped on Soy St w a suspect.<br />\n<br />\n城市廣播 City Broadcasting Channel (CBC)<br />\n<br />\n1937 防暴警察於豉油街突然向另一邊衝前，多名記者從後跟上。然而，警員突然向一眾記者施放胡椒噴霧，包括本台在內的多名記者受波及，不少義務急救員更於混亂期間受傷倒地。"},{"pid":"b2edf9334ce9fa90bc272e8a59408e290ff00054","tid":2010484,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:19:04.000Z","msg":"20:15 警員於登打士街警告在場人士或違限聚令 要求人群散開"},{"pid":"c7bb2cb14e30b052f6d0185f96a8b9337c825e9a","tid":2010484,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"又咪圍捕，不過一邊唔郁由另一邊推晒過去"},{"pid":"e13e3c42907a46d2eb267f3d59dcb9903664998d","tid":2010484,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c7bb2cb14e30b052f6d0185f96a8b9337c825e9a","tid":2010484,"uid":66221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"又咪圍捕，不過一邊唔郁由另一邊推晒過去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"提返大家 太耐無行街"},{"pid":"7766b8d7595a027250de344c9b74750f12d86855","tid":2010484,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T12:21:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" 